<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19003</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老棕熊巴鲁开始教毛克利森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他告诉男孩儿去哪儿找好吃的坚果，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>教他当蝙蝠白天睡觉的时候，不要去惹它。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利还学到跳进水里之前要提醒水蛇注意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每天，巴希拉都会来检查毛克利的进步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利太棒了！”巴鲁高兴地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56069</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他既擅长爬树，又擅长游泳，还擅长跑。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁让毛克利努力学习。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有一天，毛克利觉得学腻了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁一训斥毛克利偷懒，毛克利就跑掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个男孩儿哪儿去了？”巴希拉到的时候问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁叹了口气。“他生气跑掉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个人类孩子太年轻了。”巴希拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许他的大脑太小，记不住所有这些事情。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，他不小了，会被杀掉的！”巴鲁回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“所以我要教他森林法则。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在学所有的森林语言。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些会保护他，让他在这里一直安全。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许吧。”巴希拉伸直一只爪子，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>欣赏着自己尖尖的趾甲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等我们找到毛克利，我让你见识见识他的语言能力。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁说，“可是，谁知道他什么时候回来呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就在这儿呢！”一个声音从上面传来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利从一棵树干上滑下来看着巴鲁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145374</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我回来是因为巴希拉，我还是对你很生气，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145374</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你这个又肥又老的巴鲁！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让巴希拉看看你怎么说那些森林语言。”巴鲁说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哪一个？我知道所有的森林语言。”毛克利得意洋洋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160872</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，优秀的模范生。”巴鲁逗毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“像狮子那样说话，怎么样？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利低声说：“我们是一个血统的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好。”巴鲁说，“现在，像鸟那么说话。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利发出一声老鹰的叫声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉很惊讶。“现在说蛇语吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘶——！”毛克利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他为自己的表现鼓掌，然后跳到了巴希拉的背上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他用后脚跟踢了踢黑豹的侧腰，看着巴鲁做了个鬼脸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>214087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，你会感激我的。”巴鲁嘟囔道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>214087</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219584</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“巴鲁，你怎么学会所有语言的？”巴希拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219584</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>棕熊骄傲地拍着自己大大的、毛茸茸的肚子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我跟大象哈提学的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，毛克利踢了一下巴希拉，抓紧了他的毛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿！”巴希拉说，“小心我的肋骨。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，我会拥有一个我自己的部落。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利骄傲地说，“我会带领所有动物穿过森林。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254493</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我会一整天又玩儿又吃。”他大笑道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254493</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，我会朝老巴鲁扔树枝和土。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗖！巴鲁的大熊掌把毛克利从巴希拉背上打了下去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“毛克利！”巴鲁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你听起来就像只猴子，你和他们一起玩了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利躺在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他朝巴希拉看去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉的眼神变得很冷。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子们没有规矩。它们又粗鲁又愚蠢。”巴鲁说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>294468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“离他们远点儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>294468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利抽了抽鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301967</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你以前对我不好，但猴子们对我很热情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301967</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们从树上下来陪我玩儿，还给我坚果吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴鲁不屑地哼了一声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们说总有一天，我会成为他们的首领。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315345</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利又特意加了一句。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他们没有首领。”巴希拉厉声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>326319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，他们撒谎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>326319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332228</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听好了，毛克利。”巴鲁的声音像打雷一样低沉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332228</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>337818</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猴子们住在树上。他们不停地吹牛、闲聊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>337818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>341024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们不在猴子们喝水的地方喝水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>341024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>343679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们不去猴子们去的地方。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>343568</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利静静地躺着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346318</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>350000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们不理他们。”巴鲁补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>350000</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“即使他们朝我们头上扔坚果！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>358252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，坚果从树上掉了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>358252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>365832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一大群猴子放声大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>